"See [dining philosophers](dining-philosophers.md) for a description of the "
"problem."
msgstr "Xem [dining triết gia](dining-philosophers.md) để biết mô tả vấn đề."

#: src/concurrency/async-exercises/dining-philosophers.md
msgid ""
"As before, you will need a local [Cargo installation](../../cargo/running-"
"locally.md) for this exercise. Copy the code below to a file called "
